{"id":232852939,"title":"窮畫家之小確幸系列作品--《緣起不滅》","content":"https://i.imgur.com/FUD4qjv.jpg\n自從學會畫畫之後，\n舉凡家裡缺什麼東西沒錢買時，\n就會獨自默默地躲起來畫這些鬼東西，\n滿足一下假物質帶來的視覺快感......\n\n說真的，\n上次畫了《三顆雞蛋》後，\n因為餓到忘了畫平底鍋、煎蛋鏟子、調味料及餐具，\n兩人最終還是只能痴痴地望著那三顆雞蛋乾瞪眼，\n所以......\n那三顆蛋並沒有真正解決我和老婆大人飢寒交迫的窘境！\n\n為了感恩她完全沒有任何一絲絲的抱怨，\n與多年來的相知相守，\n以及在背後默默地支持我，\n我當下便決定要送份禮物給她，\n謝謝她的不離不棄。\n\n但伸手再度摸摸口袋，\n依舊沒有摳摳可以買禮物送她，\n於是只好再返回畫室，\n拿起那藍色筆桿的鐵人鉛筆，\n趕緊為她畫了一張人像素描，\n聊表鄙人不足為道之小小心意......","excerpt":"自從學會畫畫之後，舉凡家裡缺什麼東西沒錢買時，就會獨自默默地躲起來畫這些鬼東西，滿足一下假物質帶來的視覺快感......，說真的，上次畫了《三顆雞蛋》後，因為餓到忘了畫平底鍋、煎蛋鏟子、調味料及餐具，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"c82dae3f-28ba-4aae-961d-c754e6ccd37a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-08T15:55:19.556Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-08T15:55:19.556Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":18,"tags":[],"topics":["手繪","素描","心情","愛情","生活"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"手作","forumAlias":"handicrafts","school":"中國文化大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":17},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/FUD4qjv.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"fc2b3c38-a01d-4b37-ac96-e041a15875a5","url":"https://i.imgur.com/FUD4qjvl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/FUD4qjvl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/FUD4qjvl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-08T15:55:19.556Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-08T15:55:19.556Z"},{"id":"fc2b3c38-a01d-4b37-ac96-e041a15875a5","url":"https://i.imgur.com/FUD4qjv.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/FUD4qjv","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/FUD4qjvl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-08T15:55:19.556Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-08T15:55:1